      "writtenOn": "2025-12-23T13:48:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If there were files owned by `FRONTEND_FILES_OWNER` and there are no files owned by `FRONTEND_FILES_OWNER` in the new PS, shouldn\u0027t we keep the vote?\n\nOr we are assuming the worst? I.e.: no files have owner associated hence the change will never be reviewed.",
